  "text": "The Storage Unit is composed of the pallet to be monitored and a dedicated L/H/T node placed on the surface. It communicates via ZigBee with the Central Unit. The dedicated node is used to precisely define the product shelf life, because the use of parameters derived mathematically from the Environmental Monitoring Unit, can lead to an avoidable propagation of errors [CITATION_1] .",
